# paad/ holds build artifacts: deployable game builds alongside private
# paad: review output (*-reviews/). Default-deny everything, then whitelist
# the games we actually want deployed. Use /paad/* (not /paad/) so the !
# re-includes work — git won't descend into a fully-ignored directory.
/paad/*
!/paad/tramp-freighter/
!/paad/zork/
/docs/

